cs.SE, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.PL, cs.SD 

Reasoning: 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on building a dataset and a predictive model for estimating defectiveness of source code, which are key topics in software engineering. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper uses machine learning algorithms to train the predictive model. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper evaluates different machine learning algorithms and parameter configurations to pick the best model. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper analyzes coding style information and programming language constructs used in the source code. 
- cs.SD (Software Development) is also possible as the paper's contributions can be useful for several automated software engineering areas such as bug localization, code review, and program repair.
